changelog.title: CISSP Laws & Regulations Reference
changelog.description: Comprehensive reference for GDPR, HIPAA, SOX, GLBA, CCPA, PCI-DSS and international privacy laws with quiz.

changelog.title: Security Models Visualizer
changelog.description: Interactive visualization of Bell-LaPadula, Biba, Clark-Wilson, and Brewer-Nash security models.

changelog.description: SDLC phases with security integration, DevSecOps, SAST/DAST/IAST testing, OWASP Top 10, CMM/CMMI levels.

changelog.description: BIA, BCP, DRP tools with RTO/RPO/MTD calculators, hot/warm/cold site comparison, backup strategies.
